<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Hi evil brothers and sistas.<br>
Well i think its about time i posted here cause so many posts made me wanna bonk the author. All this bithcing about SKs suck, HT is a joke etc is a fuging joke. <br>
OK so u are a shadow knight, do u really understand the powers u have? Some may say we got the weak necro magic: ok lets analyze that, what spells do we really need, u are a meele class rigth! First we have a snare spell and a fear spell, YOU are the dots while bonking the mob. Plus we have helluva lot more hp. U can take a few nukes, necros cant. <br>
Next, we have BOTH invisable and vs undead CHEERS. The debuffs and ac str steal is an awesome thing to, while pallys for example get self buffs do they decrease the mobs abilty : NO. <br>
We can also lessen downtime while soloing  by lifetap green stuff or just suck it out someone elses mob, evil grin. At lev 50 we get a 280, i repeat 280 dmg lifetap. The quest is hard BUT with eq so old u can prolly buy all the stuff from other players for a decent amount. And if u are rich u can use a few Reapier of the dead effect complete healing to be on feet at once. Post 50 we get some insane spells (heck and ull be pleased) ie at 52 an awesome pet, jeez im still 51, very slow btw, sighs...<br>
And now to the HT issue that makes me pi789ing mad, i say HT is awesome if u know how to use it, it saved my ass so many times. HT isnt and was never meant to be a 10 k dmg effect, what it can do however is first TAUNT for evac situation, second in close figths ive noticed that HT makes the mob turn and start to run when using it in the last fifth part or so in the mobs life (mobs with a lot of HPs that is), even if dmg doesnt max out. <br>
Laff, im tired, can u tell!?<br>
Only dowside i can think of with SK is that so many spells are magic based and gets resist a lot, more by players less by NPCs. U dont really fear a warrior in duel post 50, atleast he will resist 3 out 4...<br>
SO to sum up, i know i made no sence at all, chuckle.<br>
What do we have here : the shadoknight.<br>
1. U are a decent tank that taunts better than a warrior, yes i claim that, post 50 mobs at least. Spells agro more then taunt.<br>
2. A decent meele with all spells needed to solo. Bandage and regen bp for those who can afford makes it even more effective.<br>
3. U dont die much, latter part in life when u learned how to use FD and thats REALLY gerat for a meele class specially in Kunark, u have been slayed by wurm, LOADING PLEASE WAIT, u shout need a port for cr pls.../w 1player in Neriak....get the point!<br>
3. An awesome dueler, HT, 280 lifetap, a decent pet in latter part of life...cancel magic spells etc and if u need and can afford unlimited lay on hands in reapier of the dead. Buff ure magic resist and eat chanters and necros for breakfast eventhough i hate to admit that necros (and shammys ,shivers) have many diff types of spells (disease, posion etc ) stop hiding behind that pet chicken rofl.<br>
SO don not give up on ure low level sk just cause warriors and even rangers ROFL outdanmges u. Dont gibe up casue u only can hit for 20 and no slam as a small race, the int will be SO nice later on. Hang in there and be a rare goodlooking class. Hang in there and only roll with 1 other sk in plane of fear for that nice black umbral. <br>
U will be good, and with the nongroup issue. group with friends that are good players and know SKs are a good class...<br>
Thats all folks might post more if i see some replies.<p>

Zytl 51 Reaver on Povar.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
